            "type": "text",
            "text": "Measuring and Reporting Test Coverage"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Adversarial testing coverage should be tracked against the attack surface map, not just by test count. The goal is to confirm that every identified risk area has at least one test case that exercises it."
          }
        ]
      },
